{"tid":1550703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於大埔黨鐵站 我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:59:11.000Z","uid":205087,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"92b10931f90bf862780c9e97e8086136b21e4caf","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">話咩狗推走唔該退個啲 唔該同我收聲！</span><br />\n<br />\n我係大埔人 當時就係現場 原先有隻狗好好禮貌咁同我地講話走架喇 宜家收緊隊 3分鐘後真係走哂 <br />\n<br />\n見班狗走 我地都慢慢諗住散 <br />\n<br />\n但過咗唔夠10分鐘 有人大叫有狗 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大班狗突然番泥 一落車就追人咬！追人打</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係事實全部 信不信由你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班狗真係冇個好人 信一成都死！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我仲心諗真係有狗聽得明人話 原來我錯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c13e5d5c8313903a271e1e10b782a6cb466386e","tid":1550703,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41efbe5c93177001a4ad5ecb864a413020fd8423","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"b02b4c3dba48c36aefb3063b63977725bb383656","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3048e6fcf5e7cb954f6546872a9c254334ce7f14","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"de7de742021a41fe6652b0ef3c54e9d7bad65166","tid":1550703,"uid":224213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"班狗真係好撚仆街"},{"pid":"07183c56f139f55ddddfc5d6e5bb246f13fa1051","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"3cedd61db3a0c3430afa45cb1692a4a9ca827a7f","tid":1550703,"uid":68598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"估唔到仲有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9413d2c1c56a0528f6d2c1729908460fb775d098","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"f19849e4a682498023a071423879e32cc13c9378","tid":1550703,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"煩左少少但希望大家幫手推<br />\n<br />\n香港人新精神：打狗救人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550408</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地要變"},{"pid":"d24e7f6066ed60e57f338112b7da29575056b435","tid":1550703,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6133829166558ea2b1fe15eda76b89be64d60bcc","tid":1550703,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"同政府一樣"},{"pid":"635500c4a8f4bdba7d2d86d96509cc078c2e0a49","tid":1550703,"uid":201975,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6670aa8479930bb77b6fd4f4b914282d2e3bd84","tid":1550703,"uid":213597,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"099035deb6c3581c8c461ea90fe982068c019676","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"有圖有真相<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GHSjdmY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGHSjdmY.jpg&h=5093c77b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A81snfB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA81snfB.jpg&h=b7d1dbf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1c3b1309dc934d5220101c9412a56eada5ce56c","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"繼續6/10"},{"pid":"39acfcf5c95bd3ba565e66b1da6cff680f77770f","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"07ba5e9445aa71637cd9e913e42e54da22f3957a","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"2c5b3f6993bad9cfc1646a43d8aeb7f56aef3d0b","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:54.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"8a330a64718715e2e4b5ad499409c005f533e107","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:19:04.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"461acf154aa46e7ccb98f5db68b29a51ddb698c7","tid":1550703,"uid":621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"信狗一成 命仔都凍過水呀"},{"pid":"3d9a16f61986749b41dfb0a8ff8626239888cd33","tid":1550703,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:19:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=f061ce87\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"dc0e32a9a588ca47db201593d1fc4f0976fb68d4","tid":1550703,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197d2064046d3f2e398348cb0a069fdf7ddfe158","tid":1550703,"uid":205087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"唔係有記者係隔離 我應該俾狗打左"},{"pid":"0bcb3b031cc0516063793e396df98e08581354c5","tid":1550703,"uid":120324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e6670aa8479930bb77b6fd4f4b914282d2e3bd84","tid":1550703,"uid":213597,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:21:48.000Z","msg":"點解未見你死嘅咁"}]}